NAME

    HPC::Runner::Command::Utils::ManyConfigs - Load many layered configs

SYNOPSIS

      use Moose;
      with 'HPC::Runner::Command::Utils::ManyConfigs';
    
      #Specify search_paths with --search_path
      #Specify config base with --config_base

DESCRIPTION

    HPC::Runner::Command::Utils::ManyConfigs are just some helper utilities
    to make it easier to layer config files

    It is in the HPC::Runner::Command namespace, but it is meant to be
    portable for any MooseX::App.

